                "description": "Transposed virtual displacement vector, used in the dot product with force vectors in the weak form.\n",
                "justifications": ":\nExplicitly appears as \u03b4u^T in equations (3) and (8), where the transpose of the virtual displacement vector is used in inner products with stress and body force terms."
